title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) per capita in Lithuania 2024
yAxis: GDP per capita in U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, containing a total of 30 data points.
Overall GDP per capita in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2008 and 2009.
The highest GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, of value 25936.96 was reached at Year 2024
The lowest GDP per capita in U.S. dollars, of value 1845.67 was reported at Year 1995
